args: Phew. That's the foundation put together.\nNext up is...
Heh heh! Now it's your turn to be ＂it!＂
Now I'm curious, too. Let's go find out!
Whoa! That kid's building something\non top of that tree!
Ooh, I know! It's a SECRET HIDEOUT!
Huh? Oh, it's a couple of runts.\nMust be from town.
Hey! You're building a secret base, right?!
I knew it! That's so cool! Can I help?!
Um, I want to help too, if that's okay...
(Sorry, but I wasn't really lookin' to\nspend my day babysitting here, fellas.)
(Bah. Guess it wouldn't be very\nmature of me to just run 'em off.)
(Besides, I know how it feels to get left out\nin the cold on the whole building-a-secret-\nhideout dream.)
All right, all right. C'mon,\nlet's get this thing put together.
Yesss! This is gonna be AWESOME!
But some of this work's dangerous. You\nguys are just helpin' with the easy bits,\nunderstood?
Yeah, sure! Here, I'll carry this lumber up\nthe tree!
Whoa, whoa. Easy, tiger! You plannin' on\nclimbing a ladder with an armful of wood?\nThat's just ASKIN' for a nasty fall!
Then, um... How do we get it up there?
First you climb up, THEN you haul the\nlumber up with a rope.
If somebody stays down there and helps\nlift it from below, it'll go up twice as easy.
Whoa... That makes so much sense.\nHey, you're pretty smart!
Picked that one up back in my mercenary\ndays. We scaled a cliff face to get the drop\non the enemy, then...
You know what, never mind.\nLook, don't sweat the details.
Now c'mon. This thing ain't gonna build\nitself!
And so construction proceeded without a hitch.\nThe base was soon completed, and somehow\nnobody got hurt in the process!
Heh... How's that for a vista?\nI'd say we built a damn fine base, boyos!
I still can't believe we built something\nthis amazing all by ourselves.
Yeah! We just did exactly what he\nsaid and it came together like magic!
From now on, you're our leader, Ranzal!
Sorry, but I'm not lookin' to be boss\nof the babies, kid. Kinda embarrassing,\ny'know?
Aw, I think it'd be really great.\nWith you leading us, every day\nwould be an adventure!
Right?! I wanna do more stuff like this!
(Rgh... The puppy dog eyes get me\nevery time.)
Fiiine, sure, whatever you want.\nGuess I'm sultan of the squirts now.
(Just don't count on me stickin' around\nforever, kids.)
(Still, it's better than twiddling the ol'\nthumbs until gremlin mode wears off.)
